{
  "page": "Library Tower",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><div class=\"thumb tright\"><div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:352px;\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:Alaric_Stark_and_Alysanne_Targaryen_by_Amuelia.jpg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/thumb/6/66/Alaric_Stark_and_Alysanne_Targaryen_by_Amuelia.jpg/350px-Alaric_Stark_and_Alysanne_Targaryen_by_Amuelia.jpg\" width=\"350\" height=\"344\" class=\"thumbimage\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/6/66/Alaric_Stark_and_Alysanne_Targaryen_by_Amuelia.jpg/525px-Alaric_Stark_and_Alysanne_Targaryen_by_Amuelia.jpg 1.5x, /images/thumb/6/66/Alaric_Stark_and_Alysanne_Targaryen_by_Amuelia.jpg/700px-Alaric_Stark_and_Alysanne_Targaryen_by_Amuelia.jpg 2x\" /></a>  <div class=\"thumbcaption\"><div class=\"magnify\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:Alaric_Stark_and_Alysanne_Targaryen_by_Amuelia.jpg\" class=\"internal\" title=\"Enlarge\"></a></div><a href=\"/index.php/Alaric_Stark\" title=\"Alaric Stark\">Alaric Stark</a> and <a href=\"/index.php/Alysanne_Targaryen\" title=\"Alysanne Targaryen\">Alysanne Targaryen</a> by Amuelia ©</div></div></div>\n<p>The <b>Library Tower</b><sup id=\"cite_ref-Racok69.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Racok69.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup><sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasos80.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasos80.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup> or <b>library tower</b><sup id=\"cite_ref-Ragot14.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Ragot14.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup> is a tower at <a href=\"/index.php/Winterfell\" title=\"Winterfell\">Winterfell</a> which contains the castle's library. It is maintained by Septon <a href=\"/index.php/Chayle\" title=\"Chayle\">Chayle</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Ragot9.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_4-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Ragot9.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Layout\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Layout</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#History\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">History</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#Recent_Events\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Recent Events</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#A_Game_of_Thrones\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\"><i>A Game of Thrones</i></span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#A_Clash_of_Kings\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3.2</span> <span class=\"toctext\"><i>A Clash of Kings</i></span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-6\"><a href=\"#A_Storm_of_Swords\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3.3</span> <span class=\"toctext\"><i>A Storm of Swords</i></span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-7\"><a href=\"#Quotes\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Quotes</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Layout\">Layout</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Library_Tower&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Layout\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>The Library Tower is located across the bailey from the <a href=\"/index.php/Great_Keep_(Winterfell)\" title=\"Great Keep (Winterfell)\">Great Keep</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Ragot14.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Ragot14.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup> Snug and warm, the Library Tower has high windows.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Ragot9.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_4-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Ragot9.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup> The tower contains shelves, benches, and a table. <a href=\"/index.php/Winterfell\" title=\"Winterfell\">Winterfell</a>'s library contains more than a hundred books<sup id=\"cite_ref-Racok6.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_5-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Racok6.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-5\">&#91;5&#93;</a></sup> and includes rare volumes, including a complete copy of <i><a href=\"/index.php/Engines_of_War\" title=\"Engines of War\">Engines of War</a></i> by <a href=\"/index.php/Ayrmidon\" title=\"Ayrmidon\">Ayrmidon</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Ragot9.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_4-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Ragot9.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup> Curling around the tower's exterior are steep stone steps.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Ragot9.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_4-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Ragot9.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup> \n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"History\">History</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Library_Tower&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: History\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>The library of <a href=\"/index.php/Winterfell\" title=\"Winterfell\">Winterfell</a> has been collected by <a href=\"/index.php/House_Stark\" title=\"House Stark\">House Stark</a> for centuries.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Ragot14.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Ragot14.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup> When Queen <a href=\"/index.php/Alysanne_Targaryen\" title=\"Alysanne Targaryen\">Alysanne Targaryen</a> visited Winterfell in <a href=\"/index.php/Years_after_Aegon%27s_Conquest#Year_58_After_the_Conquest\" title=\"Years after Aegon&#39;s Conquest\">58&#160;AC</a>, Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Alaric_Stark\" title=\"Alaric Stark\">Alaric Stark</a> allowed her to browse the modest castle library.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabjaehaerys_and_alysanne_-_their_triumphs_and_tragedies.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_6-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabjaehaerys_and_alysanne_-_their_triumphs_and_tragedies.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-6\">&#91;6&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Recent_Events\">Recent Events</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Library_Tower&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Recent Events\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"A_Game_of_Thrones\"><i>A Game of Thrones</i></span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Library_Tower&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: A Game of Thrones\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<p><a href=\"/index.php/Tyrion_Lannister\" title=\"Tyrion Lannister\">Tyrion Lannister</a> explores the library during his visit to <a href=\"/index.php/Winterfell\" title=\"Winterfell\">Winterfell</a> and reads a book about the changing of the seasons. Meanwhile, Septon <a href=\"/index.php/Chayle\" title=\"Chayle\">Chayle</a> falls asleep while reading a history of Grand Maester <a href=\"/index.php/Aethelmure\" title=\"Aethelmure\">Aethelmure</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Ragot9.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_4-4\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Ragot9.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup> Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Eddard_Stark\" title=\"Eddard Stark\">Eddard Stark</a> allows Tyrion to borrow a few rare volumes for his journey north to the <a href=\"/index.php/Wall\" title=\"Wall\">Wall</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Ragot13.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_7-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Ragot13.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-7\">&#91;7&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p><a href=\"/index.php/Catspaw\" title=\"Catspaw\">An assassin</a> sets the Library Tower on fire as a distraction for his attempt to kill <a href=\"/index.php/Bran_Stark\" title=\"Bran Stark\">Bran Stark</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Ragot14.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Ragot14.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"A_Clash_of_Kings\"><i>A Clash of Kings</i></span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Library_Tower&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: A Clash of Kings\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<p>Bran and Chayle sort through scrolls rescued from the library fire.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Racok4.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_8-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Racok4.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-8\">&#91;8&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>After the <a href=\"/index.php/Sack_of_Winterfell\" title=\"Sack of Winterfell\">sack of Winterfell</a>, Bran sees a shallow steaming lake beneath the Library Tower and a crack in its side.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Racok69.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Racok69.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"A_Storm_of_Swords\"><i>A Storm of Swords</i></span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Library_Tower&amp;action=edit&amp;section=6\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: A Storm of Swords\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<p><a href=\"/index.php/Sansa_Stark\" title=\"Sansa Stark\">Sansa Stark</a> includes the Library Tower while making a snow castle of Winterfell while at the <a href=\"/index.php/Eyrie\" title=\"Eyrie\">Eyrie</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasos80.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasos80.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Quotes\">Quotes</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Library_Tower&amp;action=edit&amp;section=7\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Quotes\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<blockquote class=\"templatequote\" style=\"border-left:none;\"><div class=\"templatequotetext\"><p>The library tower's on fire.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Ragot14.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-4\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Ragot14.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup></p></div><div class=\"templatequotecite\"><cite>&#8212;<a href=\"/index.php/Robb_Stark\" title=\"Robb Stark\">Robb Stark</a> to <a href=\"/index.php/Catelyn_Stark\" title=\"Catelyn Stark\">Catelyn Stark</a></cite></div>\n</blockquote>\n<blockquote class=\"templatequote\" style=\"border-left:none;\"><div class=\"templatequotetext\"><p>Across the bailey, long tongues of flame shot from the windows of the library. She watched the smoke rise into the sky and thought sadly of all the books the <a href=\"/index.php/House_Stark\" title=\"House Stark\">Starks</a> had gathered over the centuries.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Ragot14.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-5\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Ragot14.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup></p></div><div class=\"templatequotecite\"><cite>&#8212;thoughts of <a href=\"/index.php/Catelyn_Stark\" title=\"Catelyn Stark\">Catelyn Stark</a></cite></div>\n</blockquote><div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Racok69.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Racok69.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">1.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Racok69.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\">1.1</a></sup></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Clash_of_Kings\" title=\"A Clash of Kings\">A Clash of Kings</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Clash_of_Kings-Chapter_69\" title=\"A Clash of Kings-Chapter 69\">Chapter 69</a>, Bran VII.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rasos80.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rasos80.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\">2.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rasos80.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-1\">2.1</a></sup></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Storm_of_Swords\" title=\"A Storm of Swords\">A Storm of Swords</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Storm_of_Swords-Chapter_80\" title=\"A Storm of Swords-Chapter 80\">Chapter 80</a>, Sansa VII.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Ragot14.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Ragot14.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-0\">3.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Ragot14.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-1\">3.1</a></sup> <s